---
---

<section
  class="mx-auto grid max-w-7xl grid-cols-1 items-center gap-16 px-6 pb-32 pt-24 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:px-10 lg:pt-32"
>
  <!-- Left — content -->
  <div class="fade-in-up">
    <!-- Badge -->
    <div
      class="mb-8 inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-border bg-secondary px-3 py-1.5"
    >
      <span class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary"></span>
      <span class="font-mono text-xs text-muted-foreground">
        Agora com suporte a Ollama
      </span>
    </div>

    <!-- Headline -->
    <h1
      class="max-w-[540px] text-4xl font-bold leading-[1.08] tracking-[-0.04em] text-foreground md:text-5xl lg:text-[3.5rem]"
    >
      Escreva menos.<br />
      Entregue mais.<br />
      <span class="text-primary">Deixa a IA cuidar do PR.</span>
    </h1>

    <!-- Subtext -->
    <p
      class="mt-6 max-w-[480px] text-base leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground"
    >
      CLI tools para gerar descrições de PR e cards de teste no Azure DevOps.
      Suporta OpenRouter, Groq, Gemini e Ollama. Um comando. Zero burocracia.
    </p>

    <!-- CTAs -->
    <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3">
      <a
        href="#install"
        class="rounded-md bg-foreground px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-background transition-all duration-200 hover:bg-foreground/90 active:scale-[0.98] active:translate-y-px"
      >
        Instalar agora
      </a>
      <a
        href="https://docs-pr-tools.nitodev.com.br"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener"
        class="rounded-md border border-border px-5 py-2.5 text-sm text-muted-foreground transition-all duration-200 hover:border-foreground/20 hover:text-foreground active:scale-[0.98]"
      >
        Ver documentação
      </a>
    </div>

    <!-- Trust -->
    <p class="mt-6 font-mono text-xs text-muted-foreground/50">
      Sem cadastro. Funciona no terminal. Código aberto.
    </p>
  </div>

  <!-- Right — decorative terminal preview -->
  <div class="fade-in-up stagger-2 hidden lg:block">
    <div class="rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-5 shadow-[0_24px_48px_-12px_oklch(0.72_0.15_162/0.06)]">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2 pb-4">
        <span class="h-2.5 w-2.5 rounded-full bg-muted-foreground/20"></span>
        <span class="h-2.5 w-2.5 rounded-full bg-muted-foreground/20"></span>
        <span class="h-2.5 w-2.5 rounded-full bg-muted-foreground/20"></span>
      </div>
      <div class="font-mono text-xs leading-[1.8] text-muted-foreground">
        <p class="text-muted-foreground/40">~/project on <span class="text-primary">feat/streaming</span></p>
        <p class="mt-1 text-foreground">$ create-pr-description</p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-muted-foreground/60">&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="text-primary">done</span> Contexto git coletado</p>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground/60">&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="text-primary">done</span> Descrição gerada via groq</p>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground/60">&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="text-primary">done</span> PR criado com reviewers</p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-foreground/70">PR #847 criado com sucesso</p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-primary/70">$ <span class="animate-pulse">_</span></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
